I would like to be one of the first to congratulate you for the wonderful
new look of the AIO magazine.
{p} {p}
I think it is one of the best front ends I have seen to a magazine.
{p} {p}
i.e.    simple to use.{p}
        has pictures and text on screen pages.{p}
        does not require any complicated installations.{p}
        fast.{p}
        runs with other programs.{p}
{p} {p}
I particularly liked the articles section taking the !!!! out of the PC. I
have heard so many of these lately that I did not think I would laugh any
more until I read that article.
